While I have experience with Figma and Canva for basic design tasks, I am eager to improve my graphic design skills to better visualize game structures and mechanics. Through this internship, I aim to deepen my knowledge of game theory, procedural content generation, and mathematical modeling in game design. This opportunity will help me bridge the gap between theory and practical implementation, equipping me with the tools to create mentally engaging and strategically rich games in the future.



